sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant KycController
    participant RegisterCustomerService
    participant CustomerRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Client->>KycController: POST /api/v1/customers
    KycController->>RegisterCustomerService: register(fullName, email)
    RegisterCustomerService->>RegisterCustomerService: Valider données
    RegisterCustomerService->>RegisterCustomerService: Créer Customer
    RegisterCustomerService->>CustomerRepository: save(customer)
    CustomerRepository->>DB: INSERT customer
    CustomerRepository-->>RegisterCustomerService: Customer
    RegisterCustomerService-->>KycController: Customer
    KycController-->>Client: 200 + RegisterCustomerResponse
